    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-567_127934_000002_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/567/127934/567_127934_000002_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-567",
        "content": "mr Quarterpage himself came to the door, and recognized Spargo immediately.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-567_127934_000002_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/567/127934/567_127934_000002_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-567",
        "content": "Nothing would satisfy him but that the two should go in; his family, he said, had just retired, but he himself was going to take a final nightcap and a cigar, and they must share it.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-567_127934_000003_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/567/127934/567_127934_000003_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-567",
        "content": "\"For a few minutes only then, mr Quarterpage,\" said Spargo as they followed the old man into his dining room.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-567_127934_000003_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/567/127934/567_127934_000003_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-567",
        "content": "\"We have to be up at daybreak.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-567_127934_000003_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/567/127934/567_127934_000003_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-567",
        "content": "And-possibly-you, too, would like to be up just as early.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-567_127934_000004_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/567/127934/567_127934_000004_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-567",
        "content": "mr Quarterpage looked an enquiry over the top of a decanter which he was handling.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-567_127934_000005_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/567/127934/567_127934_000005_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-567",
        "content": "\"At daybreak?\" he exclaimed.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-567_127934_000006_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/567/127934/567_127934_000006_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-567",
        "content": "We have managed to get an order from the Home Secretary for the exhumation of Chamberlayne's body: the officials in charge of it have come down in the same train with us; we're all staying across there at the 'Dragon.' The officials have gone to make the proper arrangements with your authorities.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-567_127934_000007_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/567/127934/567_127934_000007_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-567",
        "content": "\"God bless me!\" exclaimed mr Quarterpage.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-567_127934_000007_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/567/127934/567_127934_000007_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-567",
        "content": "And this other young gentleman?\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-567_127934_000008_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/567/127934/567_127934_000008_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-567",
        "content": "Spargo looked at Breton, who had already given him permission to speak. \"mr",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-567_127934_000008_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/567/127934/567_127934_000008_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-567",
        "content": "Quarterpage,\" he said, \"this young gentleman is, without doubt, john Maitland's son.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-567_127934_000008_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/567/127934/567_127934_000008_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-567",
        "content": "And I'm sure you'll shake hands with him and wish him well.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-567_127934_000009_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/567/127934/567_127934_000009_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-567",
        "content": "mr Quarterpage set down decanter and glass and hastened to give Breton his hand.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-567_127934_000010_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/567/127934/567_127934_000010_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-567",
        "content": "\"My dear young sir!\" he exclaimed.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-567_127934_000010_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/567/127934/567_127934_000010_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-567",
        "content": "\"That I will indeed!",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-567_127934_000010_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/567/127934/567_127934_000010_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-567",
        "content": "And as to wishing you well-ah, I never wished anything but well to your poor father.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-567_127934_000010_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/567/127934/567_127934_000010_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-567",
        "content": "He was led away, sir, led away by Chamberlayne.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-567_127934_000010_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/567/127934/567_127934_000010_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-567",
        "content": "God bless me, what a night of surprises!",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-567_127934_000010_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/567/127934/567_127934_000010_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-567",
        "content": "Why, mr Spargo, supposing that coffin is found empty-what then?\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-567_127934_000011_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/567/127934/567_127934_000011_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-567",
        "content": "\"Then,\" answered Spargo, \"then I think we shall be able to put our hands on the man who is supposed to be in it.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-567_127934_000012_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/567/127934/567_127934_000012_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-567",
        "content": "\"You think my father was worked upon by this man Chamberlayne, sir?\" observed Breton a few minutes later when they had all sat down round mr Quarterpage's hospitable hearth.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-567_127934_000012_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/567/127934/567_127934_000012_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-567",
        "content": "\"You think he was unduly influenced by him?\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-567_127934_000013_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/567/127934/567_127934_000013_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-567",
        "content": "mr Quarterpage shook his head sadly.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-567_127934_000014_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/567/127934/567_127934_000014_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-567",
        "content": "\"Chamberlayne, my dear young sir,\" he answered.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-567_127934_000014_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/567/127934/567_127934_000014_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-567",
        "content": "Nobody knew anything about him until he came to this town, and yet before he had been here very long he had contrived to ingratiate himself with everybody-of course, to his own advantage.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-567_127934_000014_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/567/127934/567_127934_000014_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-567",
        "content": "I firmly believe that he twisted your father round his little finger.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-567_127934_000014_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/567/127934/567_127934_000014_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-567",
        "content": "Dear me-dear me!--and you really believe that Chamberlayne is actually alive, mr Spargo?\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-567_127934_000015_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/567/127934/567_127934_000015_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-567",
        "content": "Spargo pulled out his watch.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-567_127934_000015_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/567/127934/567_127934_000015_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-567",
        "content": "\"We shall all know whether he was buried in that grave before another six hours are over, mr Quarterpage,\" he said.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-567_127934_000016_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/567/127934/567_127934_000016_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-567",
        "content": "And the people actively concerned went quietly to work, and those who could do nothing but watch stood around in silence.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-567_127934_000017_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/567/127934/567_127934_000017_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-567",
        "content": "It seems a strange, strange thing to interfere with a dead man's last resting place-a dreadful thing.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-567_127934_000018_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/567/127934/567_127934_000018_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-567",
        "content": "\"If there is a dead man there,\" said Spargo.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-567_127934_000019_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/567/127934/567_127934_000019_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-567",
        "content": "He watched all that was done.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-567_127934_000019_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/567/127934/567_127934_000019_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-567",
        "content": "At first there was nothing to do but wait, and Spargo occupied himself by reflecting that every spadeful of earth thrown out of that grave was bringing him nearer to the truth; he had an unconquerable intuition that the truth of at any rate one phase of the Marbury case was going to be revealed to them.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-567_127934_000020_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/567/127934/567_127934_000020_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-567",
        "content": "\"They're down to it!\" whispered Breton.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-567_127934_000021_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/567/127934/567_127934_000021_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-567",
        "content": "Presently they all went and looked down into the grave.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-567_127934_000022_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/567/127934/567_127934_000022_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-567",
        "content": "james CARTWRIGHT CHAMBERLAYNE Born eighteen fifty two Died eighteen ninety one",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-567_127934_000023_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/567/127934/567_127934_000023_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-567",
        "content": "Spargo turned away as the men began to lift the coffin out of the grave.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-567_127934_000024_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/567/127934/567_127934_000024_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-567",
        "content": "\"And yet-what is it we shall know if----\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-567_127934_000025_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/567/127934/567_127934_000025_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-567",
        "content": "\"If-what?\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-567_127934_000026_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/567/127934/567_127934_000026_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-567",
        "content": "But Spargo shook his head.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-567_127934_000028_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/567/127934/567_127934_000028_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-567",
        "content": "It seemed to Spargo that each man grew slower and slower in his movements; he felt that he himself was getting fidgety. Then he heard a voice of authority.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-567_127934_000029_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/567/127934/567_127934_000029_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-567",
        "content": "\"Lift the lid off!\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-567_127934_000030_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/567/127934/567_127934_000030_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-567",
        "content": "A man at the head of the coffin, a man at the foot suddenly and swiftly raised the lid: the men gathered round craned their necks with a quick movement.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-567_127934_000031_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/567/127934/567_127934_000031_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-567",
        "content": "Sawdust!",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-567_127934_000032_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/567/127934/567_127934_000032_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-567",
        "content": "The coffin was packed to the brim with sawdust, tightly pressed down. The surface lay smooth, undisturbed, levelled as some hand had levelled it long years before.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-567_127934_000033_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/567/127934/567_127934_000033_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-567",
        "content": "The sound of the laughter broke the spell. The chief official present looked round him with a smile.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-567_127934_000034_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/567/127934/567_127934_000034_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-567",
        "content": "\"It is evident that there were good grounds for suspicion,\" he remarked.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-567_127934_000034_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/567/127934/567_127934_000034_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-567",
        "content": "\"Here is no dead body, gentlemen.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-567_127934_000034_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/567/127934/567_127934_000034_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-567",
        "content": "See if anything lies beneath the sawdust,\" he added, turning to the workmen.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-567_127934_000034_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/567/127934/567_127934_000034_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-567",
        "content": "\"Turn it out!\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-567_127934_000035_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/567/127934/567_127934_000035_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-567",
        "content": "He, too, laughed.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-567_127934_000036_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/567/127934/567_127934_000036_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-567",
        "content": "\"The coffin's weighted with lead!\" he remarked.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-567_127934_000036_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/567/127934/567_127934_000036_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-567",
        "content": "\"See!\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-567_127934_000038_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/567/127934/567_127934_000038_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-567",
        "content": "\"Done it cleverly,\" he remarked, looking round.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-567_127934_000038_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/567/127934/567_127934_000038_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-567",
        "content": "\"You see how these weights have been adjusted.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-567_127934_000038_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/567/127934/567_127934_000038_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-567",
        "content": "When a body's laid out in a coffin, you know, all the weight's in the end where the head and trunk rest.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-567_127934_000038_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/567/127934/567_127934_000038_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-567",
        "content": "Clever!\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-567_127934_000039_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/567/127934/567_127934_000039_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-567",
        "content": "\"Clear out all the sawdust,\" said some one.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-567_127934_000039_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/567/127934/567_127934_000039_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-567",
        "content": "\"Let's see if there's anything else.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-567_127934_000040_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/567/127934/567_127934_000040_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-567",
        "content": "There was something else.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-567_127934_000040_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/567/127934/567_127934_000040_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-567",
        "content": "The legal gentlemen present immediately manifested great interest in these.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-567_127934_000041_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/567/127934/567_127934_000041_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-567",
        "content": "The first bundle of papers opened evidently related to transactions at Market Milcaster: Spargo caught glimpses of names that were familiar to him, mr Quarterpage's amongst them.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-567_127934_000041_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/567/127934/567_127934_000041_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-567",
        "content": "He was not at all astonished to see these things.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-567_127934_000041_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/567/127934/567_127934_000041_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-567",
        "content": "He gave a hasty glance at these and drew Breton aside.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-567_127934_000042_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/567/127934/567_127934_000042_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-567",
        "content": "\"Didn't Aylmore say that the real culprit at Cloudhampton was another man-his clerk or something of that sort?\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-567_127934_000043_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/567/127934/567_127934_000043_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-567",
        "content": "\"He did,\" agreed Breton.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-567_127934_000043_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/567/127934/567_127934_000043_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-567",
        "content": "\"He insists on it.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-567_127934_000044_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/567/127934/567_127934_000044_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-567",
        "content": "\"Then this fellow Chamberlayne must have been the man,\" said Spargo. \"He came to Market Milcaster from the north.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-567_127934_000044_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/567/127934/567_127934_000044_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-567",
        "content": "What'll be done with those papers?\" he asked, turning to the officials.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-567_127934_000045_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/567/127934/567_127934_000045_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-567",
        "content": "\"We are going to seal them up at once, and take them to London,\" replied the principal person in authority.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-567_127934_000045_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/567/127934/567_127934_000045_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-567",
        "content": "\"They will be quite safe, mr Spargo; have no fear.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-567_127934_000046_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/567/127934/567_127934_000046_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-567",
        "content": "\"You don't, indeed!\" said Spargo.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-567_127934_000046_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/567/127934/567_127934_000046_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-567",
        "content": "\"But I may as well tell you that I have a strong belief that they'll reveal a good deal that nobody dreams of, so take the greatest care of them.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-567_127934_000047_000000",
